message:
Hello everybody!!! 
I hope you all are having an amazing summer so far!!! I have taken on the responsibility and am pleased to host the Minneapolis hub for summer connect with Cru this year! So if you are still interested in watching the live stream on Thursday nights at 7pm, it's free to sign up, or just come on over to the lighthouse! We don't have space for parking but there should be street parking. Message me if you have any questions or text me at 763-234-5586! Thanks everyone!
